This README file contains information on the contents of the
meta-kiss-ti layer.

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

Dependencies
============

  Internal dependency on meta-kiss layer

  URI: https://git.openembedded.org/openembedded-core
  branch: scarthgap

  URI: git://git.yoctoproject.org/meta-arm
  branch: scarthgap

Patches
=======

Please submit any patches against the meta-kiss-ti layer as patches to
feedback@bootlin.com or as github pull requests at
https://github.com/bootlin/yocto-kiss

Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-kiss-ti layer to your build
 II. Misc


I. Adding the meta-kiss-ti layer to your build
=================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-kiss-ti'

II. Misc
========

This layer provides an example of the simplest, but realistic and working,
Yocto/OpenEmbedded setup for end products. It is not useful as is, but
rather as a reference on how a layer can be written without unnecessary
complications.
